lyrics:
[Verse]
At Glynn's Sunday afternoon party, hearts ignite
Music blares, shadows dance, under fading light
Loud cheers fill the air, we're ready to ignite
Basking in the rock 'n' roll, we're feeling so alive

[Chorus]
Oh, we sway and we sing
In the chaos, we find our peace
At Glynn's Sunday afternoon party
Where our souls are finally released
